    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Support Ticket Triage System\\n\",\"**NLP Project 81 of 100** — Route support tickets by urgency and team using text classification.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Build a multi-output classifier (urgency + team assignment).\\n\",\"2. Use TF-IDF + ML for fast triage.\\n\",\"3. Evaluate routing accuracy.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\\nfrom sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, classification_report\\nfrom sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"templates = {\\n    ('Billing','High'): ['I was charged twice','Unauthorized charge on my account','Refund not processed after 30 days'],\\n    ('Billing','Low'): ['How do I update payment method','Where can I see my invoices','What payment methods do you accept'],\\n    ('Technical','High'): ['System is completely down','Cannot access my account at all','Data loss after update','Critical error blocking work'],\\n    ('Technical','Low'): ['How to change settings','Feature question about dashboard','Minor display issue'],\\n    ('Account','High'): ['Account hacked need help now','Locked out of account urgently','Personal data breach suspected'],\\n    ('Account','Low'): ['How to change email address','Password reset question','Update profile information'],\\n}\\n\\nrows = []\\nfor (team, urgency), texts in templates.items():\\n    for t in texts * 30:\\n        noise = rng.choice(['please help','urgent','question','need assistance','hello'])\\n        rows.append({'text': f'{noise} {t}'.lower(), 'team': team, 'urgency': urgency})\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(rows).sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}')\\nprint(df[['team','urgency']].value_counts())\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"X_train, X_test, y_train_team, y_test_team = train_test_split(\\n    df['text'], df['team'], test_size=0.2, random_state=SEED)\\n_, _, y_train_urg, y_test_urg = train_test_split(\\n    df['text'], df['urgency'], test_size=0.2, random_state=SEED)\\n\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=5000, ngram_range=(1,2))\\nX_tr = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train); X_te = tfidf.transform(X_test)\\n\\n# Team classifier\\nlr_team = LogisticRegression(max_iter=500, random_state=SEED)\\nlr_team.fit(X_tr, y_train_team)\\ny_pred_team = lr_team.predict(X_te)\\nprint('=== Team Routing ===')\\nprint(f'Accuracy: {accuracy_score(y_test_team, y_pred_team):.4f}')\\nprint(classification_report(y_test_team, y_pred_team))\\n\\n# Urgency classifier\\nlr_urg = LogisticRegression(max_iter=500, random_state=SEED)\\nlr_urg.fit(X_tr, y_train_urg)\\ny_pred_urg = lr_urg.predict(X_te)\\nprint('=== Urgency Classification ===')\\nprint(f'Accuracy: {accuracy_score(y_test_urg, y_pred_urg):.4f}')\\nprint(classification_report(y_test_urg, y_pred_urg))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **TF-IDF + LogReg routes tickets effectively** with high accuracy.\\n\",\"- **Urgency detection is harder** than team routing due to subtle language differences.\\n\",\"- **For production, combine with keyword rules** for critical escalation.\\n\",\"- **Monitor routing accuracy over time** and retrain as ticket patterns change.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
